name: Diagnosis
description: Diagnosis set according to genetic test

name: OMIM page for the diagnosis description/  diagnosis description elsvwhere
AGE when sent for genetic testing
description: Age of the patient when the genetic test was done (y-years, m-months), relevant for diagnostics delay

name: Spontaneous abortions
description: {Yes}/{No}/{Unknown}. If yes, how many, type number.

name: Indication for refferal: HPO descriptive
description: Clinical symptoms, List of descriptive HPO
example: Global developmental delay HP:0001263, Esodeviation 8 Convergent strabismus) HP:0020045, Hypotonia HP:0001252, Alien limb phenomenon HP:0032506, Abnormal involuntary eye movements HP:0012547,

name: Age at Onset
description: The age group in which disease manifestations appear, Age when symptoms begin, (y-years, m-months)

name: Measurements
description: (for metabolic disease), measurements of biochemical analysis
example: Urine metabolic screen - in expected range, urine organic acid test - in expected range

name: Clinical centre of refferal
description: Name of the Clinical center which sent patient for genetic testing

name: Varijant(s)
description: Number of detected variants in the gene

name: Zigosity
description: Zigosity in relation to another pathogenic variant in the same gene

name: Secondary/Incidental findings
description: If other genes not related to ID or metabolic disease were detected, type the name of that gene, otherwise type NO

name: Transcript
description: Accession numbers for the transcritp (NCBI) - related to secondary/incidental findings

name: Variant name 1
description: variant description - related to secondary/incidental findings

name: Location of VCF (IMGGI server, External HD, etc)
